<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
Library Initialization

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
Perform general initialization with limited argument parsing.

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
Almost always one run eva_init() at the top of main and forgets about it.
But sometimes you wish to separate the parsing and the initialization 
so these routines give you more fine-grained control,
by separating the parsing into eva_init_info_parse_args() and 
the real initialization into eva_init_raw().
</para>

